('Who is the best point of contact for GKKIntern business onboarding?', 'The business email info@gkkintern.in is the best starting point. Add your objective and timeline in the first message.', 'Contact', 'GKKIntern'),
('Is there any registration fee for GKKIntern applicants?', 'No official joining or registration fee is required for application submission. Avoid paying anyone outside official channels.', 'Policy', 'GKKIntern'),
